And I thought
they were eyedrops

26:03.959 --> 26:06.709
and I put ear drops in my eyes.
- [gasps]

26:06.709 --> 26:08.000
- My friend asked me
the other day,

26:08.000 --> 26:09.417
do you have any breath spray?

26:09.417 --> 26:11.709
So I give it to him
and he goes,

26:11.709 --> 26:14.292
