26:14.292 --> 26:15.667
- Put in his mouth?

26:15.667 --> 26:17.959
- I've been using it
in my mouth for a week.

26:17.959 --> 26:20.584
- She's eccentric as well.
- Yes.

26:20.584 --> 26:22.542
- I mean,
we're all so different.

26:22.542 --> 26:23.751
And we share the same
sense of humor.

26:23.751 --> 26:25.501
- Nobody knows the real Kyle,
you see?

26:25.501 --> 26:27.918
- Oh, really?
- Kyle is very eccentric.

26:27.918 --> 26:29.083
- Let me ask you this.

26:29.083 --> 26:32.501
Who designed the lampshade hat
we saw in the finale?

26:32.501 --> 26:34.167
- Oh, Lorna Murray.

26:34.167 --> 26:35.876
And I love it.
I have it in all colors.

26:35.876 --> 26:38.083
- You have it in all colors?
- I do. I love her.

26:38.083 --> 26:39.834
- I call it
the coffee filter hat.

26:39.834 --> 26:40.876
- Oh, yeah.

26:40.876 --> 26:42.417
- It does look like that.
