relationship to Hilton Hotels?

27:44.167 --> 27:47.250
- My father-in-law
and Rick's grandfather--

27:47.250 --> 27:49.209
- Was Conrad Hilton.
- Right.

27:49.209 --> 27:51.083
- The man who founded
Hilton Hotels.

27:51.083 --> 27:52.709
- Who founded Hilton Hotels.
- Okay.

27:52.709 --> 27:55.959
- So this is Rick's
family business?

27:55.959 --> 27:57.834
- Rick does not have anything
to do with it at all.

27:57.834 --> 27:59.167
- He does not?
- No, no, no.

27:59.167 --> 28:00.959
- It was sold?
- Yes.

28:00.959 --> 28:03.125
- This is about probably
ten years ago.

28:03.125 --> 28:04.334
- Got it.

28:04.334 --> 28:05.751
- Evelyn from Pittsburgh said,

28:05.751 --> 28:09.083
"Ladies, who would trust Kathy
to cut your hair?"

28:09.083 --> 28:10.501
- Oh, hell no.
- No.

28:10.501 --> 28:11.792
- I would.
- Rinna would?

28:11.792 --> 28:13.334
- Absolutely not!
- Yeah, I'd let her.

28:13.334 --> 28:15.083
