to do dental work?

28:15.083 --> 28:17.709
- Not dental.
- With a nail file?

28:17.709 --> 28:18.792
- That's where you draw
the line, right?

28:18.792 --> 28:21.584
- I draw the line.
- And I do COVID tests as well.

28:21.584 --> 28:23.167
[laughter]
- Oh, do you?

28:23.167 --> 28:24.834
- Well, I want
to leave it there.

28:24.834 --> 28:28.542
We are gonna be back with more
from Beverly Hills after this.

28:28.542 --> 28:29.626
Coming up...

28:29.626 --> 28:31.542
- Why didn't you understand

28:31.542 --> 28:35.000
that we could be concerned
being grouped in?

28:35.000 --> 28:36.751
