- Yes.
- (BLEEP).

29:55.834 --> 30:01.292
- I left La Quinta thinking,
"Something's amiss."

30:01.292 --> 30:03.834
- There's no proof to not
believe Erika, at this point.

30:03.834 --> 30:07.000
I don't know
what is going on there.

30:07.000 --> 30:08.834
I need to find out.

30:08.834 --> 30:11.876
I need to let it play out
and see what's gonna happen.

30:11.876 --> 30:14.584
- I mean, yes, I'm here
if you've lost all your money.

30:14.584 --> 30:16.000
I'm here if your husband
cheated on you.

30:16.000 --> 30:17.584
I'm here if you're
getting divorced.

30:17.584 --> 30:19.584
But if there's any connection,
you know--

30:19.584 --> 30:21.042
- Yes. If you ----ing knew--

30:21.042 --> 30:22.792
- What was going on here,
I need to know that,

30:22.792 --> 30:24.918
because guess what.
That's a very different story.

30:24.918 --> 30:27.584
- I think that we have
heard stories

30:27.584 --> 30:30.042
that, to me, don't add up.

30:30.042 --> 30:32.459
- Tom got in a car accident by
our house and broke his ankle.

30:32.459 --> 30:33.709
- Oh, no.

30:33.709 --> 30:36.042
- So I've been dealing with
the biggest baby on the planet.

30:36.042 --> 30:37.334
He's fine.

30:37.334 --> 30:39.334
- Oh, my gosh.
