30:43.209 --> 30:45.417
- He was also unconscious
for 12 hours.

30:45.417 --> 30:47.250
- He was?

30:47.250 --> 30:49.501
- I know he was unconscious
for 12 hours.

30:49.501 --> 30:50.542
I mean, the head injury
that he had--

30:50.542 --> 30:52.876
- Allegedly, yeah. Mm-hmm.

30:52.876 --> 30:55.042
- Now I'm kind of like,

30:55.042 --> 30:57.501
"What else is going on
that we don't know?"

30:57.501 --> 30:59.918
- Tom's house was broken into
and he confronted the burglar

30:59.918 --> 31:01.751
and then had to go
have eye surgery.

31:01.751 --> 31:03.417
