31:05.667 --> 31:06.417
five times on the way home.

31:06.417 --> 31:07.918
Yeah, I'm under
a lot of stress.

31:07.918 --> 31:09.167
- Wait, what?

31:09.167 --> 31:12.292
- What are the statistics
that Tom

31:12.292 --> 31:15.959
and his stepson both flip cars?

31:15.959 --> 31:17.751
I would guess they're
millions and millions

31:17.751 --> 31:19.125
and millions to one.

31:19.125 --> 31:20.375
- Let me tell you something.

31:20.375 --> 31:22.667
There's lies
all over the place.

31:22.667 --> 31:26.292
- Clearly, you understand
that we are dragged into this

31:26.292 --> 31:28.209
whether we like it or not.
- We're nervous.

31:28.209 --> 31:30.042
I think some people
are nervous.

31:30.042 --> 31:32.250
- You guys, are you really
that afraid of me?

31:32.250 --> 31:35.209
- I don't trust that 100%
of what you've told us

31:35.209 --> 31:36.375
