a very sweet day.

32:00.876 --> 32:04.042
And I'm going to remember
those who were with me,

32:04.042 --> 32:07.667
and I'm going to remember
those who were against me.

32:07.667 --> 32:09.083
Trust me.

32:09.083 --> 32:12.667
♪

32:12.667 --> 32:16.042
- So who is for you?
