32:25.125 --> 32:26.125
- Uh-huh.

32:26.125 --> 32:28.125
- So what's the score so far?

32:28.125 --> 32:29.375
- I'm gonna keep that
to myself.

32:29.375 --> 32:31.417
I think it's pretty--
