Especially after PK
had been so kind

33:27.334 --> 33:29.584
and we'd worked so hard
on our relationship.

33:29.584 --> 33:31.000
That sucked.

33:31.000 --> 33:33.542
- That night, specifically,
I felt so bad.

33:33.542 --> 33:36.167
First of all, PK and Mo,
you know,

33:36.167 --> 33:38.125
they're like brothers.
