- To add to that.
- Because we do care about you.

33:46.626 --> 33:49.375
- Because I was receiving
a new piece of information.

33:49.375 --> 33:50.792
And this was about your son.

33:50.792 --> 33:52.375
She sent her son
who's a police officer

33:52.375 --> 33:53.542
to check on him.

33:53.542 --> 33:55.709
The son went home,
was driving home.

33:55.709 --> 33:58.000
Her son lives somewhere
where it was snowing,

33:58.000 --> 34:01.125
